data.description:
Welcome to your charming 3-2 retreat in the heart of Texas! As you step inside, the open concept design and inviting color palette welcome you alongside natural light that floods the space through expansive sliding doors, seamlessly bringing the peaceful outdoors in.

The heart of this home is undoubtedly the large kitchen, a culinary haven featuring a center island perfect for entertaining. The kitchen is adorned with modern aesthetics, including a beautiful stone arch surrounding the range, stainless steel appliances, and contemporary fixtures. The master suite is a luxurious escape, complete with an ensuite bathroom boasting a double vanity, a spacious walk-in shower, and closet space galore. Two additional bedrooms and a nice sized hall bath offer comfort and style.

Outside, a wrap-around porch invites you to soak in the beauty of country living as you take in the panoramic views of your very own slice of Texas. The fenced-in backyard ensures privacy, and a large shed and RV storage cater to all your needs. This property also features an above-ground pool where you can cool off during hot Texas summers.  

Escape the hustle and bustle of city life and embrace the tranquility of this property. With its perfect blend of modern amenities, thoughtful design, and a touch of Texas charm, this home really has it all.
